quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  99,1,When the earth is shaken with a mighty quake
  99,2,and the earth throws out its burdens
  99,3,"and man says, “What is the matter with it?”"
  99,4,On that Day it will recount all its news
  99,5,"because your Lord has inspired it [to do so]"
  99,6,On that Day all people will come forward in separate groups to be shown their deeds
  99,7,So whoever does an atom’s weight of good will see it
  99,8,and whoever does an atom’s weight of evil will see it